Itau USA Asset Management Inc. Key Developments

Excel Funds Management Inc. Announces Sub-Adviser Appointment
Apr 28 17
Excel Funds Management Inc. announced that Itau USA Asset Management Inc. has been retained to provide sub-advisory services to Excel Investment Counsel Inc., Excel Funds' affiliate, in respect of a portion of Excel Emerging Markets Fund's portfolio. This appointment is to become effective on April 28, 2017. Itau USA Asset Management Inc., the U.S. arm of Itau Asset Management, will be responsible for Excel Emerging Market Fund's Latin American-based investments.


