Itau Usa Asset Management Inc 

Share with your friendsYour NameYour EmailRecipient EmailEnter a MessageI read this article and found it very interesting, thought it might be interesting for you. The article is called Itau Usa Asset Management Inc and is was published by Octafinance.com at http://www.octafinance.com/hedge-funds/itau-usa-asset-management-inc/.CaptchaSubmitItau Usa Asset Management Inc is a New York-based institutional investor with more than $1.26 billion AUM in September, 2014. This fund invests only a small percentage of its assets in equities and options. Taken from Itau Usa Asset Management latest Adv, the fund reported to have 20 full and part-time employees. Among which 9 performing investment advisory and research functions. The institutional investor had between 11-25 clients.






